.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-LISTFORWARDS-COUNT-DAILY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-listforwards-count-daily \- FEAT-2879 node-listforwards-count-daily
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-listforwards-count-daily
.SH DESCRIPTION
Count of settled forwards today (UTC) (FEAT-2879).
.PP
Queries settled forwards via lightning-cli listforwards and counts entries
whose resolved_time falls within the current UTC calendar day.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
